Apologies for dropping back in.  I had no idea the Doc still had that tremendous bug up his pompous, know-it-all ass for me.  I certainly didn't expect him to go bonkers a-g-a-i-n, as I have been off-line for quite a while and then, when I got back on, read how the Doc had changed and how &quot;everybody&quot; was now getting along much better- more respectful, more civil, etc.  And I read where now you vets are about to give the Doc medals and shit.  Phew!  What a difference a few months can make, huh?  I don't wanna mess that up by giving The Great Monopolizer of this (these) sites more ammunition (as if he needed it).  Art, I love ya. Live long and prosper.    
